1. Purpose

Provides cosmological initial conditions for the ET
See the documentation for detailed instructions on choosing perturbations and other parameters
Enjoy!

2. Citation

Please cite Macpherson, Lasky, & Price (2017; arXiv:1611.05447) if using FLRWSolver in any publications
